| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4664 — Recovery Inhibition (blacklock)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e74dfabb-6bfa-58b1-aca1-d1aa9837fa4e"
